<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Suggestion Approved</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333333;
        }
        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555555;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777777;
        }
        .regards {
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .regards p {
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Hello <%= receiverName %>,</h2>

        <p>We are pleased to inform you that your suggestion has been approved. Thank you for helping us improve our services!</p>

        <h3>Details of your suggestion:</h3>
        <p><strong>Your Suggestion:</strong> <%= suggested_text %></p>
        <p>If you have any further questions or suggestions, feel free to reach out to us.</p>

        <div class="regards">
            <p><strong>Best regards,</strong><br>Our Team</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email.</p>
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Our Company Name. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
